      "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/validation/vr-hemolysis-piv-comparison",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "PIV velocity field comparison — FDA pump nominal geometry",
      "description": "Comparison of CFD-predicted velocity fields against particle image velocimetry (PIV) measurements at five flow-speed operating points. GCI-based discretization uncertainty bounded at 4.2% for all QoIs. RH index predictions within 12% of experimental values across all operating points.",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/morrison/activity/piv-cfd-comparison-study-2023",
